03:12:11.040 --> 03:12:12.920
but there's hundreds of other

03:12:12.920 --> 03:12:15.340
instances where security researchers'

03:12:15.660 --> 03:12:17.060
time and resources had

03:12:17.060 --> 03:12:21.520
