03:12:26.860 --> 03:12:32.280
This erosion of trust is going to make fewer talented hackers bother spending their time

03:12:32.280 --> 03:12:37.220
at all to find and report bugs, which is going to make the world's most widely used operating

03:12:37.220 --> 03:12:42.960
system that much more vulnerable, especially with so much of it being vibecoded these days.

